Package: cogcache
Title: COG Tile Cache with Rust Decode
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Michael", "Sumner", email = "mdsumner@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fetch and decode Cloud Optimised GeoTIFF tiles via HTTP range
    requests, with a Rust backend for decompression and predictor undo.
    Tiles are catalogued and cached in DuckDB. This is a proof-of-concept
    for a Rust-native warper architecture.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc
Config/rextendr/version: 0.4.2
